url = f'https://jira.tap4fun.com/rest/api/2/search?{params}'
req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={'Authorization': f'Basic {auth}'})
data = json.loads(urllib.request.urlopen(req, context=ctx).read().decode('utf-8'))
```

